<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.3">
<l>piṇivaḷa rākkai nīṅkaniṉ ṟēttap perunila maruḷiṉmu ṉaruḷi</l>
<l>yaṇivaḷar kuṟaḷā yakaliṭam muḻutu maḷantavem maṭikaḷtam kōyil</l>
<l>kaṇivaḷar vēṅkai neṭunila mataṉil kuṟavartam kavaṇiṭait turanta</l>
<l>maṇivaḷar cāral māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart; we will worship at Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">on whose slope appear gems</l>
<l>Which hill folk hurl from their slings in the broad land of the kino trees</l>
<l rend="indent">that appear in the pastures,</l>
<l>The temple of our god who, previously with grace,</l>
<l rend="indent">having bestowed [to us] the vast earth to bless [us] always</l>
<l>To be free of the body where disease appears,</l>
<l rend="indent">measured this whole, vast space as a dwarf</l>
<l rend="indent">on whom ornaments appeared.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
